Package ispd.motor.queues.centers

Class Processing

java.lang.Object
ispd.motor.queues.centers.Processing
All Implemented Interfaces:
Service
Direct Known Subclasses:
CloudMachine, CloudMaster, GridMachine, GridMaster, VirtualMachine
public abstract class Processing extends Object implements Service
Classe abstrata que representa os servidores de processamento do modelo de fila, Esta classe possui atributos referente a este ripo de servidor, e indica como calcular o tempo gasto para processar uma tarefa.

    • Processing

      protected Processing (String id, String owner, double computationalPower, int coreCount, double loadFactor, int machineNumber)
      Constructor which specifies the configuration of processing server, specifying the id, owner, computational power, core count, load factor and machine number.


      Using this constructor the energy consumption is set as default to 0.

      Parameters:
      id - the id
      owner - the owner
      computationalPower - the computational power
      coreCount - the core count
      loadFactor - the load factor
      machineNumber - the machine number
      See Also:
      • for specify the energy consumption
